<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:30.170 --> 00:01:33.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[melancholic music]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:33.140 --> 00:01:38.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:39.470 --> 00:01:41.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- He should still be home
right around this time.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:45.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[receiver clicks]</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beeping]</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:47.770 --> 00:01:48.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm?</b></Default>

c0000011
00:01:49.900 --> 00:01:51.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What is it, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It seems like Kaede's gotten
her memories back.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:55.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really?
- I wouldn't call you unless</b></Default>

c0000014
00:01:55.780 --> 00:01:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was positive.
- Of course not.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:01:58.540 --> 00:02:00.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm planning on having her
checked out at the hospital now.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you come?
- Sure thing.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:05.330 --> 00:02:07.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It seems she has no
recollection of the period</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:07.630 --> 00:02:09.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she had amnesia.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:11.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The current situation
is a little difficult for her</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:12.010 --> 00:02:14.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to grasp for now,
but after a while,</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:14.550 --> 00:02:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as more things come up,</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:15.970 --> 00:02:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she will start to notice
the gaps in her memory.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:18.350 --> 00:02:20.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be best to admit her</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:20.180 --> 00:02:22.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for observation
until this settles.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:22.390 --> 00:02:23.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We'll be counting on you,
then.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:26.270 --> 00:02:29.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I seriously don't think that
there's anything actually wrong</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:29.230 --> 00:02:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with me, though.
- You're really Kaede,</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:30.940 --> 00:02:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my little girl?
[crying]</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:32.860 --> 00:02:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:33.990 --> 00:02:35.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>D--Dad, why are you crying?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:35.910 --> 00:02:38.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]
I'm fine. It's just--</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:38.580 --> 00:02:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're kinda makin' me feel
embarrassed over here.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:41.620 --> 00:02:43.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpers]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:43.540 --> 00:02:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's nothing you need
to cry over, really.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:46.170 --> 00:02:48.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
Where you goin'?</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:49.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just the bathroom.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:02:54.880 --> 00:02:57.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sniffling]</b></Default>

c0000038
00:02:59.850 --> 00:03:02.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:02.770 --> 00:03:05.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wailing]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:05.940 --> 00:03:07.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:07.900 --> 00:03:10.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:16.950 --> 00:03:18.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was she gonna go back
to the zoo</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:18.450 --> 00:03:20.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and see the pandas again?</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:20.580 --> 00:03:22.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you were gonna get
your money's worth</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:22.330 --> 00:03:24.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the annual pass,
didn't you?</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:24.750 --> 00:03:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you could even go
to school tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:27.210 --> 00:03:30.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you thought you could.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:30.880 --> 00:03:33.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede just said that to me!</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:34.090 --> 00:03:36.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:39.890 --> 00:03:41.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not this.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:41.350 --> 00:03:42.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not now, dammit!</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:43.180 --> 00:03:45.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give me a break!
What the hell is this?</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:45.770 --> 00:03:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Any of this?</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:50.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:51.650 --> 00:03:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're going to be all right,
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:57.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:59.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, that is my name.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:59.200 --> 00:04:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that I'm here,</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:00.530 --> 00:04:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>everything's going
to be all right.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking]
I'm opening the door.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're still changing,
then it's an accident.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:12.340 --> 00:04:13.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaking]</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:14.130 --> 00:04:15.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:16.130 --> 00:04:18.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's going to take a while
for the bath to get hot.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:19.590 --> 00:04:21.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you stay like that
you're going to catch a cold.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:24.220 --> 00:04:26.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, put your hands up in
the air.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:33.860 --> 00:04:35.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're okay.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:37.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All the bleeding seems
to have stopped.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:38.450 --> 00:04:39.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you want me
to take your pants</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:39.700 --> 00:04:40.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and underwear off as well?</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:41.950 --> 00:04:43.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can do that on my own.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll leave your change
of clothes out here.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:49.410 --> 00:04:51.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shoko-san.
- What is it?</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I just...</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:55.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't do anything.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:56.090 --> 00:04:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not the case at all.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:58.130 --> 00:05:00.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> I'd say it was a valiant effor,
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:01.550 --> 00:05:03.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What could you even know
about this situation?</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:04.350 --> 00:05:05.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can tell what
you're thinking.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:05.970 --> 00:05:07.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That there may have been more</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:07.180 --> 00:05:08.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you could have done
for Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:08.730 --> 00:05:10.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand that sentiment.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:11.140 --> 00:05:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> What it's like to regret things
like that.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:16.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am Shoko-san.
I can see through it all.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:16.820 --> 00:05:18.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How do you think Kaede felt?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:20.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think she held
a grudge against you?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:21.530 --> 00:05:24.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, she loved you
the whole time, didn't she?</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:25.870 --> 00:05:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Maybe, but there's still more
I could have done.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:31.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then you can do it next time
you have the opportunity.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:32.870 --> 00:05:35.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There is no "next time"
for Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:05:35.880 --> 00:05:37.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you're going to have
an attitude like that,</b></Default>

c0000093
00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:40.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then honestly I feel sorry
for her.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:05:41.260 --> 00:05:43.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This time around she was trying
so hard so that</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:43.510 --> 00:05:45.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wouldn't have anything
to regret.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:46.260 --> 00:05:48.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For Kaede, having you
by her side through it all</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:48.390 --> 00:05:50.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was her ultimate happiness.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:50.230 --> 00:05:53.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All along she was trying
 so desperately to tell you tha.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:54.350 --> 00:05:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So if her feelings hadn't
been getting through to you,</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:56.690 --> 00:05:58.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel sorry for her.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:03.780 --> 00:06:05.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>November the fifth.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:05.370 --> 00:06:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"This will be
the first diary entry.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:07.200 --> 00:06:08.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"More to come soon.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:08.660 --> 00:06:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is Kaede's diary.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:10.950 --> 00:06:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the name that my
big brother gave to me."</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:14.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:14.540 --> 00:06:15.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- "Big brother bought
this notebook</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:17.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and this pen for her as well."</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"For family, Kaede has a father,
mother, and big brother,</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:22.050 --> 00:06:24.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"but she doesn't
really understand.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:24.470 --> 00:06:27.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"They say that Kaede
has no memory.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:27.350 --> 00:06:29.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Amnesia stemming
from dissociative disorder.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:29.810 --> 00:06:33.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what the doctor said.
Complicated."</b></Default>

c0000114
00:06:33.940 --> 00:06:36.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"They say until recently Kaede
wasn't Kaede."</b></Default>

c0000115
00:06:37.690 --> 00:06:39.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They explained there was
a different Kaede</b></Default>

c0000116
00:06:39.650 --> 00:06:44.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> that Kaede used to be but Kaede
 doesn't know anything about he.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:49.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's never met this person.
It really is complicated.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:06:49.870 --> 00:06:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>December 10th.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:51.490 --> 00:06:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother and Father look like
they're having</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:53.330 --> 00:06:55.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a really tough time.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:55.460 --> 00:06:58.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Father spent his entire
hospital visit talking</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:58.210 --> 00:06:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the doctor.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:59.920 --> 00:07:03.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He kept asking the doctor,
"When will she be better?"</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:06.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does Kaede have some kind
of illness?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:07.010 --> 00:07:09.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the other Kaede's
memories return,</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:11.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what will happen
to this Kaede?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:12.310 --> 00:07:14.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that happens,
where will she go?</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:14.390 --> 00:07:16.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When she thinks about it,
she gets scared.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:17.020 --> 00:07:18.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She can't help but cry.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:20.020 --> 00:07:21.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>March 7th.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:23.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been decided
that Kaede's moving.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:07:24.030 --> 00:07:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is allowed to choose
which things she wants</b></Default>

c0000133
00:07:26.530 --> 00:07:27.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to bring with her.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:07:27.740 --> 00:07:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what big brother said.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:07:29.490 --> 00:07:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the things in this room
are unfamiliar</b></Default>

c0000136
00:07:31.990 --> 00:07:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and make her feel uneasy.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:07:33.910 --> 00:07:35.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She decided to bring
the bookshelf</b></Default>

c0000138
00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:37.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the books in it, though.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> The other Kaede must like book.
She has a lot.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:07:41.170 --> 00:07:43.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're also bringing Nasuno
with us.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:07:43.420 --> 00:07:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've arrived at our new home.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:07:45.630 --> 00:07:48.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede thinks that someday
when she is healed,</b></Default>

c0000143
00:07:48.470 --> 00:07:50.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the other Kaede will return.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:54.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So in this new home
for the sake of big brother</b></Default>

c0000145
00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:56.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who let Kaede be Kaede,</b></Default>

c0000146
00:07:56.140 --> 00:07:59.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she will do her best to become
a wonderful little sister.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:07:59.900 --> 00:08:01.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother will be entering</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>high school starting
this spring.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He will be attending</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:06.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a school called Minegahara
High School.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother has just started
a part-time job.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:12.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He'll be coming home very late
from now on.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:12.950 --> 00:08:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a little lonely,</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but Kaede must do her best
to keep Nasuno company.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:20.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother got his
first paycheck from work</b></Default>

c0000156
00:08:20.290 --> 00:08:22.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and he used it to buy
a panda DVD for me!</b></Default>

c0000157
00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:24.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pandas are wonderful!</b></Default>

c0000158
00:08:24.170 --> 00:08:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They have healing powers!</b></Default>

c0000159
00:08:26.300 --> 00:08:29.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way! Big brother
has a real live girlfriend!</b></Default>

c0000160
00:08:29.630 --> 00:08:32.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That sounds impossible,
but it's true.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:08:32.390 --> 00:08:34.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai is a really good person.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:08:34.180 --> 00:08:36.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's actually famous
and is on TV.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:08:36.810 --> 00:08:38.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>August 2nd.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:40.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother has a friend
who will be staying</b></Default>

c0000165
00:08:40.350 --> 00:08:41.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with us starting today.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:43.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her name is Rio Futaba.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:08:43.820 --> 00:08:45.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>September 2nd.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:08:45.230 --> 00:08:47.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother has become
a total playboy.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:08:47.820 --> 00:08:49.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But that's not actually true.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:51.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka turned out
to be Mai's little sister.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:54.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- "There is one thing
that Kaede knows."</b></Default>

c0000172
00:08:55.290 --> 00:08:58.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> "Big brother's been holding ono
a lot of regret.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:08:58.370 --> 00:09:00.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"He feels that when
the other Kaede was bullied,</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:03.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he was unable to do anything
to take away her pain."</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:03.790 --> 00:09:04.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- "That's why Kaede can tell</b></Default>

c0000177
00:09:07.010 --> 00:09:09.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"that if she were to disappear</b></Default>

c0000178
00:09:09.090 --> 00:09:11.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"like this then
it would happen again.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:09:11.470 --> 00:09:12.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He would regret it."</b></Default>

c0000180
00:09:13.050 --> 00:09:14.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> "Saying he couldn't do anything
for her."</b></Default>

c0000181
00:09:15.640 --> 00:09:17.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"And so..."</b></Default>

c0000182
00:09:17.470 --> 00:09:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And so Kaede decided
to write down a list of goals.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:09:21.020 --> 00:09:23.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ones to be achieved together
with big brother.</b></Default>

c0000184
00:09:23.860 --> 00:09:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even after Kaede is gone,</b></Default>

c0000185
00:09:25.690 --> 00:09:28.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede doesn't want big brother
to have any regrets.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:31.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wants him to hold
his head high knowing he</b></Default>

c0000187
00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:33.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was able to grant so many
of her dreams.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:09:33.820 --> 00:09:36.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Instead of leaving behind
sad memories,</b></Default>

c0000189
00:09:36.580 --> 00:09:39.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> she would like to leave memoris
that are fun, happy,</b></Default>

c0000190
00:09:39.330 --> 00:09:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and make you look back
and smile.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:09:41.750 --> 00:09:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> Even if Kaede is no longer her,</b></Default>

c0000192
00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if big brother smiles whenever
he remembers her,</b></Default>

c0000193
00:09:46.590 --> 00:09:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she would be so happy.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:09:48.920 --> 00:09:52.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In order for that to happen,
Kaede will do her best.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:09:52.340 --> 00:09:55.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most likely the time Kaede
has left in this world</b></Default>

c0000196
00:09:55.300 --> 00:09:56.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will soon be coming to an end.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:09:57.220 --> 00:09:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> So please give Kaede some time.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:01.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> She just needs a little longer.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:10:02.020 --> 00:10:03.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]</b></Default>

c0000200
00:10:03.190 --> 00:10:04.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks to big brother,</b></Default>

c0000201
00:10:04.810 --> 00:10:07.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede was able
to circle so many things.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:10:08.110 --> 00:10:11.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was able to step outside
 after being scared for so long.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:10:11.110 --> 00:10:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a big one!</b></Default>

c0000204
00:10:12.740 --> 00:10:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was able to go
to Mai's place to visit, too.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:10:15.620 --> 00:10:17.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she was able to ride
the train</b></Default>

c0000206
00:10:17.490 --> 00:10:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and have so much fun
at the beach.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:10:19.660 --> 00:10:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She even got to see pandas!</b></Default>

c0000208
00:10:21.910 --> 00:10:24.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was sorta cheating
but she went to school, too.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:10:25.420 --> 00:10:28.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All those things are things
to big brother.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:10:28.130 --> 00:10:31.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother has given Kaede
so much happiness.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:10:31.970 --> 00:10:35.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede is so fortunate to be
big brother's little sister.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:10:35.470 --> 00:10:37.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She has always loved him</b></Default>

c0000213
00:10:37.510 --> 00:10:39.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she will never stop
loving him.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:10:39.930 --> 00:10:42.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tomorrow she will go
to school during the day.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:10:42.850 --> 00:10:45.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [crying]</b></Default>

c0000216
00:10:45.690 --> 00:10:47.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't have to hold
it back.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:49.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's wrong for me
to be crying!</b></Default>

c0000218
00:10:49.860 --> 00:10:51.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I cry here,</b></Default>

c0000219
00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:53.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would be going against
everything Kaede wanted.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:10:53.990 --> 00:10:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She gave it everything she had.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:10:55.950 --> 00:10:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could I trample on that?</b></Default>

c0000222
00:10:57.410 --> 00:10:58.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make it all for nothing?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:10:58.830 --> 00:11:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That deep sadness you feel</b></Default>

c0000224
00:11:00.660 --> 00:11:02.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is also something Kaede gave
to you.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:11:02.910 --> 00:11:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's more precious
than you know.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:11:05.460 --> 00:11:08.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's proof of just how big
Kaede's existence was.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:11:09.210 --> 00:11:10.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000228
00:11:11.050 --> 00:11:13.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta,
you are the big brother.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:11:13.550 --> 00:11:15.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to accept it all.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:19.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000231
00:11:19.100 --> 00:11:22.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wailing]</b></Default>

c0000232
00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000233
00:11:34.780 --> 00:11:35.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000234
00:11:36.910 --> 00:11:37.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000235
00:11:41.330 --> 00:11:42.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat purrs]</b></Default>

c0000236
00:11:53.250 --> 00:11:54.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000237
00:12:01.850 --> 00:12:03.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Man, I look rough.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:12:03.350 --> 00:12:04.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stomach growls]</b></Default>

c0000239
00:12:07.270 --> 00:12:09.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[refrigerator humming]</b></Default>

c0000240
00:12:10.230 --> 00:12:13.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomping]</b></Default>

c0000241
00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:15.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000242
00:12:16.860 --> 00:12:19.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[aggressive chewing]</b></Default>

c0000243
00:12:19.820 --> 00:12:22.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

c0000244
00:12:22.830 --> 00:12:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000245
00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000246
00:12:32.340 --> 00:12:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You have one new message.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:12:35.590 --> 00:12:39.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>November 27th at 10:05 p.m.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:12:40.180 --> 00:12:41.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hi, it's me.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:43.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Was Kaede able to go
to school today?</b></Default>

c0000250
00:12:43.390 --> 00:12:45.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't mind how late it is.
Give me a call.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000252
00:12:47.430 --> 00:12:48.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone vibrating]</b></Default>

c0000253
00:12:48.810 --> 00:12:49.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000254
00:12:50.650 --> 00:12:51.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000255
00:12:52.310 --> 00:12:54.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hello.
Good morning, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:12:54.570 --> 00:12:56.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry about yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:12:56.230 --> 00:12:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was a lot going on
and I pretty much passed out.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:12:58.740 --> 00:13:00.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I didn't notice you
had called.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:13:00.450 --> 00:13:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry about it.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:13:01.990 --> 00:13:03.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happened with Kaede,
though?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:13:03.990 --> 00:13:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did she go to school during
the day?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:13:06.580 --> 00:13:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, she wasn't able
to go to school.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:13:09.370 --> 00:13:11.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> She's in the hospital right no.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:13:11.370 --> 00:13:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She actually regained
her old memories.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:13:13.580 --> 00:13:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- But she doesn't seem</b></Default>

c0000266
00:13:15.840 --> 00:13:18.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to remember anything about
the past two years.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:13:18.510 --> 00:13:20.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course that includes you,
too.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:13:21.220 --> 00:13:23.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It looks like I'll have
to reintroduce you to her.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:13:23.510 --> 00:13:24.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:13:25.010 --> 00:13:27.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, but there's nothing
to worry about.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:13:27.100 --> 00:13:28.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's completely
fine physically.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:13:28.850 --> 00:13:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just getting a checkup</b></Default>

c0000273
00:13:30.640 --> 00:13:33.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and staying so the doctors
can observe her.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:13:33.900 --> 00:13:36.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's good,
but are you all right?</b></Default>

c0000275
00:13:36.150 --> 00:13:38.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I did get a little confused
about everything yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:40.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I calmed down a lot by
morning.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:13:41.030 --> 00:13:42.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[knocking]</b></Default>

c0000278
00:13:42.700 --> 00:13:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai, have you finished
getting ready yet?</b></Default>

c0000279
00:13:45.030 --> 00:13:47.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, looks like
my ride's here.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:49.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to go.
- Okay.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:13:49.410 --> 00:13:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll talk at length
later tonight then.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:53.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you have a great shoot.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:13:53.290 --> 00:13:55.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks. See you.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cars passing]</b></Default>

c0000285
00:14:03.180 --> 00:14:04.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What happened yesterday?</b></Default>

c0000286
00:14:04.930 --> 00:14:06.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You said you had to use
the bathroom</b></Default>

c0000287
00:14:06.430 --> 00:14:07.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and never came back.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:14:07.640 --> 00:14:09.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I had terrible diarrhea.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:14:09.390 --> 00:14:11.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was becoming best friends
with the toilet bowl.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:14:11.390 --> 00:14:13.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why do you have
to be so nasty?</b></Default>

c0000291
00:14:13.310 --> 00:14:16.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Anyway, do you like pandas?
- Uh, that was random.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:14:16.940 --> 00:14:18.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you?</b></Default>

c0000293
00:14:18.270 --> 00:14:19.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, I don't hate them.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:14:20.030 --> 00:14:22.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then let's go see them
once you're discharged.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:14:22.610 --> 00:14:24.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's fine.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you're not making any sense.
- I want to go see them.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:14:27.410 --> 00:14:28.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just come with me.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:14:28.950 --> 00:14:30.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But why would you want
to go with your little sister?</b></Default>

c0000299
00:14:31.040 --> 00:14:32.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shouldn't you find a girlfriend</b></Default>

c0000300
00:14:32.250 --> 00:14:33.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and go on a date
with her instead?</b></Default>

c0000301
00:14:33.920 --> 00:14:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I already have a girlfriend.
- What? No way!</b></Default>

c0000302
00:14:36.210 --> 00:14:38.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll introduce you soon
so you'd better brace yourself.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:14:39.210 --> 00:14:41.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all speaking at once]</b></Default>

c0000304
00:14:41.170 --> 00:14:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay, first real take!
- Take one!</b></Default>

c0000305
00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you all right?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000306
00:14:48.390 --> 00:14:50.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Like, no relationship trouble?</b></Default>

c0000307
00:14:50.220 --> 00:14:52.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
I'm all right.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:14:53.390 --> 00:14:56.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the end I never saw
a single trace of Shoko-san</b></Default>

c0000309
00:14:56.650 --> 00:14:57.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after that night.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:14:58.860 --> 00:15:00.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My calls to the middle school
Makinohara haven't</b></Default>

c0000311
00:15:00.860 --> 00:15:01.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>been answered, either.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:15:02.780 --> 00:15:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what was Shoko-san's
existence?</b></Default>

c0000313
00:15:05.530 --> 00:15:06.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't make sense.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:09.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shouldn't we consider
the possibility that</b></Default>

c0000315
00:15:09.740 --> 00:15:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the older Shoko Makinohara never
actually existed to begin with?</b></Default>

c0000316
00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:15.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, that's impossible.
I'm sure of it.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:15:15.620 --> 00:15:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
But let's look at the facts.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:15:17.040 --> 00:15:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Two years ago and now,</b></Default>

c0000319
00:15:18.710 --> 00:15:21.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>both of those times you were
the only one confirmed</b></Default>

c0000320
00:15:21.130 --> 00:15:23.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have seen Shoko Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:15:23.170 --> 00:15:25.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nobody else was able
to observe her, right?</b></Default>

c0000322
00:15:25.430 --> 00:15:27.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Talking about
observation again?</b></Default>

c0000323
00:15:28.050 --> 00:15:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can put it into more
simple terms if you'd prefer.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:32.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What you saw was merely
an illusion</b></Default>

c0000325
00:15:32.350 --> 00:15:33.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you created yourself.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:15:33.850 --> 00:15:36.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The fantasy of a rascal,
you could say.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:15:40.060 --> 00:15:42.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000328
00:15:44.190 --> 00:15:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This also a fantasy?</b></Default>

c0000329
00:15:47.360 --> 00:15:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You finished filming
the whole movie already?</b></Default>

c0000330
00:15:49.450 --> 00:15:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, just for today.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:15:51.450 --> 00:15:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll take
the first bullet train in</b></Default>

c0000332
00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the morning back up to Kanazawa.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:15:55.580 --> 00:15:58.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- What? You're not happy?</b></Default>

c0000334
00:15:58.330 --> 00:16:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Of course I'm happy.
Seriously, I'm just ecstatic.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:02.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I'll make some tea.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:16:02.550 --> 00:16:04.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry about the tea.
I'll handle it.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:16:04.460 --> 00:16:06.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You go and put some clothes on.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:16:06.170 --> 00:16:08.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll catch a cold.
- Got it.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:17.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000340
00:16:17.230 --> 00:16:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, I really
was surprised to see you.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:16:19.650 --> 00:16:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you were planning
on coming back,</b></Default>

c0000342
00:16:21.190 --> 00:16:24.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you could have let me know.
Wait, Mai, that's--</b></Default>

c0000343
00:16:24.110 --> 00:16:26.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, what is this about?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:16:26.940 --> 00:16:29.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- W--well, it's, you know, uh...</b></Default>

c0000345
00:16:30.450 --> 00:16:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On the day Kaede's
memory returned,</b></Default>

c0000346
00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shoko-san suddenly
reappeared again.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:16:34.870 --> 00:16:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And after I ran into her,</b></Default>

c0000348
00:16:36.870 --> 00:16:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she saw how depressed I was
and came back here</b></Default>

c0000349
00:16:38.620 --> 00:16:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to cheer me up.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:16:39.830 --> 00:16:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I woke up the next morning,</b></Default>

c0000351
00:16:41.380 --> 00:16:43.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I noticed she left that letter
for me.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:16:43.170 --> 00:16:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, but it's not like Shoko-san
ended up staying overnight</b></Default>

c0000353
00:16:45.710 --> 00:16:47.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or anything like that.
No, hold on.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:16:47.920 --> 00:16:49.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I can't say that. Man.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:16:49.880 --> 00:16:52.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fell asleep so I don't
know exactly when she left.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:16:52.760 --> 00:16:54.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's fine, really!</b></Default>

c0000357
00:16:55.010 --> 00:16:56.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't worry.
Nothing suspicious happened.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:16:56.770 --> 00:16:58.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000359
00:16:58.730 --> 00:17:01.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That night I really did
cry myself to sleep.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:17:01.900 --> 00:17:02.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Enough.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:17:04.360 --> 00:17:06.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as you're okay,
that's all that matters.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:17:07.190 --> 00:17:09.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mai, you--
- But sorry.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:17:09.400 --> 00:17:11.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- I'll go back today after all.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:17:11.450 --> 00:17:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, wait! Go back?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:17:13.450 --> 00:17:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To Kanazawa.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:17:14.830 --> 00:17:16.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The bullet trains
are still running.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:17:17.370 --> 00:17:18.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

c0000368
00:17:18.750 --> 00:17:20.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]
Hold on a second, Mai!</b></Default>

c0000369
00:17:21.460 --> 00:17:22.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [shudders]</b></Default>

c0000370
00:17:23.330 --> 00:17:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you...</b></Default>

c0000371
00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000372
00:17:28.170 --> 00:17:30.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can't do stuff like that
for a while, okay?</b></Default>

c0000373
00:17:32.010 --> 00:17:33.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry, really.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:17:34.140 --> 00:17:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't wanna hear
you apologize.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:17:36.220 --> 00:17:38.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not why I'm dating you,
Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:17:44.730 --> 00:17:46.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's going on with you,
Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000377
00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your eyes look dead.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:17:47.730 --> 00:17:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They look the same
as usual to me.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:17:49.240 --> 00:17:51.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, they look more dead
than usual today.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:17:51.570 --> 00:17:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, if you're
not feeling well,</b></Default>

c0000381
00:17:53.410 --> 00:17:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wouldn't it be best
to just go home?</b></Default>

c0000382
00:17:55.490 --> 00:17:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, I'm fine.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:17:57.870 --> 00:17:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome.
[plates shattering]</b></Default>

c0000384
00:17:59.080 --> 00:18:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]
- [shouting]</b></Default>

c0000385
00:18:00.580 --> 00:18:02.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doin'?
Holy smokes!</b></Default>

c0000386
00:18:04.460 --> 00:18:06.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's this?
Waiting outside for me?</b></Default>

c0000387
00:18:06.710 --> 00:18:08.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's something that we need
to talk about.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:18:09.170 --> 00:18:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Save it for another time.
I'm hungry.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:13.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus I have way too much
to think about as it is.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:18:13.760 --> 00:18:15.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All you need to be thinking
about right</b></Default>

c0000391
00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>now is my big sister.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:18:16.930 --> 00:18:19.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just so you know, the
"way too much" is Mai-related.</b></Default>

c0000393
00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:21.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big sis had
to jump through hoops</b></Default>

c0000394
00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to come back from Kanazawa.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:18:22.640 --> 00:18:24.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm telling you she's
misunderstanding all</b></Default>

c0000396
00:18:24.230 --> 00:18:26.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the stuff about Shoko-san.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000397
00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:28.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think that's the issue here?</b></Default>

c0000398
00:18:28.480 --> 00:18:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is no misunderstanding.
She trusts you?</b></Default>

c0000399
00:18:31.070 --> 00:18:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then why?</b></Default>

c0000400
00:18:32.280 --> 00:18:33.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She came back because she</b></Default>

c0000401
00:18:33.570 --> 00:18:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was worried about you!</b></Default>

c0000402
00:18:35.030 --> 00:18:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knows you've been having
a rough time lately</b></Default>

c0000403
00:18:36.950 --> 00:18:38.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with all the Kaede
stuff happening.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:40.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wanted to be by your side
and cheer you up even</b></Default>

c0000405
00:18:40.660 --> 00:18:41.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a short while.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:18:42.370 --> 00:18:44.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not to mention today
was even big sis's birthday.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:18:45.250 --> 00:18:46.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait, birthday?</b></Default>

c0000408
00:18:46.580 --> 00:18:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's right here!
December 2nd!</b></Default>

c0000409
00:18:48.540 --> 00:18:49.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How do you not even know when</b></Default>

c0000410
00:18:49.750 --> 00:18:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your own girlfriend's
birthday is?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:18:52.170 --> 00:18:54.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Toyohama, lend me your phone
a second.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:18:54.260 --> 00:18:56.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Big sis is still on sight
for the shoot.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:18:56.970 --> 00:18:58.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please, just give me
the phone!</b></Default>

c0000414
00:18:58.850 --> 00:19:01.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's your plan?
- I can still make it.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:19:01.140 --> 00:19:02.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just need to get
to Omiya and catch</b></Default>

c0000416
00:19:02.640 --> 00:19:04.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a bullet train from there.
- For real?</b></Default>

c0000417
00:19:04.350 --> 00:19:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- For real.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:19:06.190 --> 00:19:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Call me when you make
it over there!</b></Default>

c0000419
00:19:08.230 --> 00:19:11.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll ask big sis where she is
without giving it away for you!</b></Default>

c0000420
00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:14.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[loud rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000421
00:19:15.030 --> 00:19:17.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic music]</b></Default>

c0000422
00:19:18.030 --> 00:19:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000423
00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:22.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:19:34.170 --> 00:19:37.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000425
00:19:40.300 --> 00:19:43.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[labored breathing]</b></Default>

c0000426
00:19:46.060 --> 00:19:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And what are you doing here,
Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:19:47.730 --> 00:19:48.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000428
00:19:49.110 --> 00:19:51.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000429
00:19:56.200 --> 00:19:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka was persistent
in contacting me</b></Default>

c0000430
00:19:58.280 --> 00:19:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I thought you might show up.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:02.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, so much for not giving
anything away.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:20:02.490 --> 00:20:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Must have really cost you
to come all the way out here.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:20:05.370 --> 00:20:06.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, yeah, a little bit.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:20:07.370 --> 00:20:08.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What about the fare back?</b></Default>

c0000435
00:20:09.380 --> 00:20:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If I don't use
the bullet train</b></Default>

c0000436
00:20:10.960 --> 00:20:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can probably make do.
- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000437
00:20:14.340 --> 00:20:17.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Ryoko,
I'm terribly sorry about this,</b></Default>

c0000438
00:20:17.590 --> 00:20:19.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but can you see if there
are any rooms open in</b></Default>

c0000439
00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:21.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the hotel the staff
are staying at?</b></Default>

c0000440
00:20:21.300 --> 00:20:22.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll check that for you.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:20:24.680 --> 00:20:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, what?
- Well...</b></Default>

c0000442
00:20:26.730 --> 00:20:29.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000443
00:20:29.100 --> 00:20:30.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For starters,</b></Default>

c0000444
00:20:30.730 --> 00:20:32.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to tell you
happy birthday.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:20:34.020 --> 00:20:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A bit late for that.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:38.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You only have 15 minutes
for your date.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And also, please get properly
cheered up by your boyfriend.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't have
to say it like that.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:20:44.030 --> 00:20:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give me a break, Ryoko.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:20:46.120 --> 00:20:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what do you think you're
smiling at?</b></Default>

c0000451
00:20:47.790 --> 00:20:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's get going.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:20:53.750 --> 00:20:56.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So you were feeling down.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:20:56.380 --> 00:20:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You seem to be
in good spirits, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:01.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry. I was adequately
depressed myself, you know.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:21:01.970 --> 00:21:03.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000456
00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:05.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, it's totally freezing.
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000457
00:21:11.100 --> 00:21:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't you say you couldn't
do stuff like this for a while?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:21:13.980 --> 00:21:16.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's cold so it's fine.
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000459
00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hooray for winter.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:21:19.570 --> 00:21:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, uh, I really am sorry
for everything.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:21:22.490 --> 00:21:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's fine now, okay?</b></Default>

c0000462
00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not fine.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to properly apologize.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:21:27.660 --> 00:21:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were so worried about me
you rushed back home all</b></Default>

c0000465
00:21:29.660 --> 00:21:30.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the way from Kanazawa.</b></Default>

c0000466
00:21:32.670 --> 00:21:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And I also need to apologize.</b></Default>

c0000467
00:21:35.210 --> 00:21:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, you came all the way
here to see me in person.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:21:37.800 --> 00:21:39.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should be honest with you.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:21:41.010 --> 00:21:42.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When everything happened,</b></Default>

c0000470
00:21:42.510 --> 00:21:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew you were going
to need someone</b></Default>

c0000471
00:21:43.720 --> 00:21:45.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be there for you,</b></Default>

c0000472
00:21:45.100 --> 00:21:47.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but when I didn't end up being
that person,</b></Default>

c0000473
00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:49.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was a shock for me.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:21:49.810 --> 00:21:53.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So yesterday--I guess now it'd
be the day before yesterday--</b></Default>

c0000475
00:21:53.940 --> 00:21:56.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's why I said
the things I said.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:21:57.690 --> 00:22:00.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta.
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000477
00:22:01.110 --> 00:22:03.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm so sorry you were scared
and suffering</b></Default>

c0000478
00:22:03.490 --> 00:22:06.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I couldn't be there
when you needed me the most.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:22:06.120 --> 00:22:07.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your presence is enough.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:22:07.990 --> 00:22:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just having you by my side
is enough to make me happy.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:22:11.210 --> 00:22:13.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But then that means I'm
not doing anything at all.</b></Default>

c0000482
00:22:13.670 --> 00:22:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And you don't need to.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what's so amazing
about it, you know?</b></Default>

c0000484
00:22:17.090 --> 00:22:18.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000485
00:22:18.250 --> 00:22:20.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I wanna be someone</b></Default>

c0000486
00:22:20.210 --> 00:22:21.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like that for you.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:22:22.680 --> 00:22:23.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:22:24.300 --> 00:22:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What is it?
- Close your eyes.</b></Default>

c0000489
